text.SourceString: Hey babe, came for some fresh bread? I just took your favorite out of the oven.
text.LocalizedString: Hey babe, came for some fresh bread? I just took your favorite out of the oven.

text.SourceString: Oh, it's you! How's your day going, darling?

text.SourceString: Hope you’re ready for some sweet treats today, babe!
